msgstr "Дедлайны задаются на каждую задачу. Подробности в разделе ``Баллы``."

#: ../../../../docs/common_information/introduction.rst:17
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Examples are provided in ``tasks/example`` tree with ``threads`` and "
"``processes/t1``..``processes/t3`` sections."
msgstr ""
"Примеры размещены в дереве ``tasks/example`` с секциями ``threads`` и "
"``processes/t1``..``processes/t3``."

#: ../../../../docs/common_information/introduction.rst:18
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In each repository, the README.md contains a link to the course "
